The paper deals with channel estimation in wideband massive MIMO systems using compressive sensing techniques. Therefore, cs.IT (Information Theory) is the most likely category as it deals with the fundamental limits of communication systems. cs.MM (Multimedia) is also likely as it deals with the transmission of large amounts of data over wireless channels. cs.SI (Social and Information Networks) is another possible category as it deals with the analysis of large-scale networks. cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture) is also possible as it deals with the design and analysis of communication networks. Finally, cs.LG (Machine Learning) is another possible category as it deals with the development of algorithms that can learn from data.
